org.springframework.geode.boot.autoconfigure.configuration.support

Class ManagerProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.geode.boot.autoconfigure.configuration.support.ManagerProperties

  • public class ManagerProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    Spring Boot ConfigurationProperties used to configure an embedded Apache Geode Manager. A Manager allows users to manage a cluster with tools like Gfsh or Pulse. The configuration Properties are based on well-known, documented Spring Data for Apache Geode (SDG) Properties.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    Properties, Locator, ConfigurationProperties
